{"tid":205181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲成日生風爛?","createTime":"2017-04-17T14:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T03:31:07.000Z","uid":86396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6dd6f2fbef3fa03dc7aa347c8eeeb6893abeda88","tid":205181,"uid":86396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:52:34.000Z","msg":"第一次發係食左用花雕煮既田雞, 後尾食福建炒飯又奶野<br />\n之後去睇西醫, 佢地話無得醫, 只可以避啲致敏原, 西醫淨係開左啲抗敏感藥<br />\n之後再去睇中醫, 佢地話我血毒, 又要唔知煲乜煲乜, 最好都係無乜用<br />\n<br />\n後尾唔知點解生生下, 聽中醫講要戒口, 戒左一年半載既牛肉 好似有無咩翻發<br />\n但呢幾日又出番黎, 一到夜晚就係咁出, 我都忍唔到係咁R, 由佢係咁生, 有無巴絲有偏方<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d41aa353c2b466f80024050cd85ab29f48f152","tid":205181,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放棄左治療<br />\n<br />\n轉左用番梘會無咁痕"},{"pid":"a38827e330b8f6442b8df68aa8050a745bc540b6","tid":205181,"uid":86396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放棄左治療<br />\n<br />\n轉左用番梘會無咁痕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打生左幾耐?"},{"pid":"bfc3570d32ebb4c126ddfb5f48cbc84d0269b5e3","tid":205181,"uid":73749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:06:16.000Z","msg":"我試過<br />\n醫生話係「尋麻疹」<br />\n過敏體質戒口戒咗三年 加上食藥<br />\n依家好咗  無生過<br />\n最緊要戒口同埋作息時間要正常 唔好捱夜<br />\n保持心情愉悅  唔好悶悶不樂<br />\n過來人嘅經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5b82650e811069b234c8f62add7a10e157c4d3","tid":205181,"uid":9653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:30:31.000Z","msg":"天氣一凍吹風即刻生<br />\n只要保番暖就會退 勁奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a5